---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Home">
  <main class="hero">
    <h1 class="creative-header name-hero">Sofia Voumvourakis</h1>
    <p class="intro-text">
      Hello! I’m a government and data science student who often finds herself asking: 
      <span class="question-italic">“To advance humanity, are we losing it?”</span> 
      I am driven to build a future where technology governance is resilient and equitable. 
      Beyond the screen, I’m creative at heart—dabbling in poetry and art—and curious 
      in practice—exploring philosophy, psychology, and global perspectives.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    height: 60vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .name-hero {
    font-size: 7rem; /* Large and artistic */
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }
  .intro-text {
    max-width: 600px;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .question-italic {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--teal-accent);
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>